            "<strong>Matt’s Claim</strong> Circles are not similar since the do not have angles or side lengths."
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "display": "teacher",
        "content": {
          "type": "Text",
          "format": "html",
          "text": [
            "<p>Circles are not polygons. However, like any other shape, circles can be scaled.</p>",
            "<p>Circles have measures, such as, the radius or diameter.</p>"
          ]
        }
